  "text": "High performance of α-D lateral flow test in knee PJI diagnosis was demonstrated [CITATION_1] . Although their data (sensitivity 87.5% and specificity 97.1%) are consistent with our results, the authors demonstrated the superiority of Synovasure™ in terms of sensitivity and negative predictive value when compared to other typical analyses (culture, synovial cell count, ESR and CRP).",
